# ITAlab project

Vite + React SPA (`src/`). Progress is local (IndexedDB). UI copy is Turkish; lesson content is Italian.

## Design sources

- Tokens / IA / voice: `design/tokens/*`, `design/ia/navigation.md`, `design/content/voice-and-tone.md`
- CSS variables live in `src/index.css` — keep them aligned with `design/tokens/`
- Design rules: `.cursor/rules/core/*` + `.cursor/rules/frontend/*` (Spencer Goldade cursor-designer, GPLv3)

## Current priorities

1. **Mobile-first responsive** — usable at 320–430px; touch targets ≥44px; safe-area for bottom nav
2. **Findability** — Continue CTA, Pratik modes, Yol units easy to discover
3. Curriculum content changes only when explicitly requested

## Constraints

- Do not remove working lesson/practice engines
- Prefer CSS in `index.css` + existing class patterns over new UI libraries
- No purple-on-white / generic AI aesthetic; keep botanical green brand
